OL,5, Amazon is taking legal action against  
OL,6, four companies it has accused of       
OL,7, deliberately flooding its shopping     
OL,8, platform with fake reviews.            
OL,10,FThree of the firms had nearly 350,000  
OL,11,Freviewers on their books.              
OL,13,FThe companies act as unofficial brokers
OL,14,Fbetween Amazon sellers and individuals 
OL,15,Fwho write reviews, the tech giant says.
OL,17,FThe reviewers get free products and a  
OL,18,Fsmall fee in return for each review,   
OL,19,Fand the firm charges the seller a fee  
OL,20,Ffor boosting its ratings on Amazon.    
